<td valign=top width=50 bgcolor="963232"><font size=4 color=white>
News</font></td>

<td>
<font size=2 color='963232'><b>January 6, 2011:</b></font>
<font size=2 color='black'>All features of Scansite are now working again! :)</font></br></br>

<font size=2 color="963232"><b>October 9, 2009:</b></font>
<font size=2 color="black">The Swiss-Prot and TrEMBL databases were updated to their Sept. 22nd 2009 releases.  This brings the number of proteins to 509,019 in Swiss-Prot and 9,325,547 in TrEMBL.</font><br><br>

<font size=2 color="963232"><b>October 8, 2009:</b></font>
<font size=2 color="black">The Scansite server will go down tonight at 10 p.m. U.S. Eastern time to update the Swiss-Prot and TrEMBL protein databases.  The update is expected to take 4 hours.</font><br><br>

<font size=2 color="963232"><b>NOTE:</b></font>
<font size=2 color="black">During heavy usage times, protein domains from Pfam may not be displayed in the Motif Scan graphics, 
because Pfam allows only one simultaneous request from the same IP address.  If this happens, 
you can retrieve the domains directly from <a href="http://128.177.18.7/search?tab=searchSequenceBlock">Pfam</a> after finding the motifs in Scansite.</font><br>

<hr noshade>

<font size=2 color="black">Read about the <a href="scansite_2.html">new features</a> of Scansite 2.0.<br>

</td></tr></table>
</td></tr>

